description:
The Character Skin Pack 2, the latest downloadable content for Party Party Time, is here!
Transform your character's appearance with over 20 different skins!
Get the party going with your favorite costume!

The Character Skin Pack 2 includes the following content:

[21 New Skins]
- 21 new skins to choose from in the Character Selection screen.
name: Character Skin Pack 2
